title: find the possible completions given a NixOS option prefix
pid: 826e7d40-b7b4-484a-874e-58b3927a7eb1
body: |2-
  Here the prefix is "system.autoUpgrade":

  [jeff@jbb-dell:~/nix/nixpkgs]$ nixos-option system.autoUpgrade
  This attribute set contains:
  allowReboot
  channel
  dates
  enable
  flags
  flake
  randomizedDelaySec
